IT WOULDN'T COME TO MY MIND

00:07:38,625 --> 00:07:42,062
TO THINK THAT I'D NEED A --
AN ADDITIONAL TOOL, RIGHT?

00:07:42,062 --> 00:07:44,364
EVEN IF IT'S MESSY,
IN MY CASE, OR...
YEAH.

00:07:44,364 --> 00:07:45,999
...YOU KNOW,
FIDGETY OR WHATEVER,

00:07:45,999 --> 00:07:47,167
