THINK THAT,

00:07:47,167 --> 00:07:49,135
"OKAY, I NEED TO
SOLVE THIS PROBLEM."

00:07:49,135 --> 00:07:52,672
AND FOR THAT REASON,
I'M OUT.

00:07:52,672 --> 00:07:54,140
ALL RIGHT,
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

00:07:54,140 --> 00:07:55,041
THANK YOU.
THANKS.

00:07:56,876 --> 00:07:59,879
I THINK WHAT YOU'VE BUILT HERE
IS REALLY COOL.

00:08:01,648 --> 00:08:05,285
ONE OF MY FAVORITE THINGS TO DO
IS ACTUALLY FEED HER

00:08:05,285 --> 00:08:06,586
AND HAVE THAT MOMENT.

00:08:06,586 --> 00:08:08,121
YEAH.

00:08:08,121 --> 00:08:11,291
BUT I THINK MY EXPERTISE
WOULD BE MORE VALUABLE TO YOU

00:08:11,291 --> 00:08:13,093
LATER DOWN THE ROAD

00:08:13,093 --> 00:08:15,695
WHEN YOU NEED TO REALLY PUSH
A MARKETING CAMPAIGN.

00:08:15,695 --> 00:08:18,031
I THINK I COULD HELP YOU
DO A LOT OF THOSE THINGS.

00:08:18,031 --> 00:08:21,568
I-I -- FRANKLY, WHEN IT COMES
TO MANUFACTURING HARD GOODS,

00:08:21,568 --> 00:08:23,737
GETTING THEM DONE
AT THE RIGHT PRICE POINT,

